io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.builder

Class ModifyMetadataTransactionBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.builder.TransactionBuilder<ModifyMetadataTransactionBuilder,ModifyMetadataTransaction>
      • io.proximax.sdk.model.transaction.builder.ModifyMetadataTransactionBuilder

  • public class ModifyMetadataTransactionBuilder
extends TransactionBuilder<ModifyMetadataTransactionBuilder,ModifyMetadataTransaction>

    builder for ModifyMetadataTransaction

    Standard use: first initialize builder by call to one of forAddress(Address), forMosaic(MosaicId) or forNamespace(NamespaceId). Then specify modifications to make via call to modifications(List) or modifications(MetadataModification...)
